pullRequest.title: Refactor stub4testtool.xsl
pullRequest.bodyText:
Refactors stub4testtool.xsl to enable the following items:

Senders in senders (#674)
Multiple receivers (#1102)

commit.message: Refactor choose to separate templates (excluding receivers/pipelines/senders)
Small XSLT fixes + refactor pipeline and receiver stubbing, and start sender refactoring (stub is not complete yet)

afterCommit.message: Small XSLT fixes + refactor pipeline and receiver stubbing, and start sender refactoring (stub is not complete yet)
